data.description: This impeccable home shows like a model with an Award winning open floor plan and beautiful views of the golf course! Why wait for new construction when you can have it all right now. Located in the Viera N. of Wickham area and only 3 minutes from I- 95 and The Avenues Shopping area. Lower taxes than a Viera home. 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, 2 oversized car garage, extended screened lanai with peaceful views!  Formal living room, dinning room, family room, kitchen with 42 inches cabinets, ''Thermodore'' appliances, open concept with island/bar, granite surfaces throughout, extended/ oversized full house width screened in terrace with a spa/hot tub, tile throughout and bedrooms with ''tempurpedic'' padding carpets.  Impact resistant windows plus hurricane shutters.  Plantation shutters throughout, custom master bedroom closet and so much more. Only a 25 minute drive to the beaches and in a great School district. Call for your appointment to tour this impeccable 2013 construction home.
